      <text class="text-lg">
        I am a well versed Information Technology Specialist, with skills that include Ubiquity Unifi Technology, practice with
        various Virtual Machine platforms including; VMware, XCP-ng, Hyper-V, TrueNAS, Proxmox-VE, Azure AD, and Amazon EC2.  Most of my previous
        expirence included working with Office365(Now Microsoft 365) as well as many other different platforms both Closed and Open Source.
      </text>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-8">
      <a class="btn" href="/cv"> My Resume</a>
